# Jobs

- Signature: `(job: Job) => void | Promise<void>`
- Jobs must go through a **service** — do not call repositories directly
- **Logger**: receive `logger: Logger` via closure or deps; use for job start/end and error traces

```typescript
// jobs/index-document.job.ts
export async function indexDocumentJob(job: Job): Promise<void> {
  const result = await documentService.index(job.data);
  if (!result.ok) throw result.error;
}
```
